  "status": "active",
  "version": 1,
  "summary": "Hierarchy & Application table rows are fixed; Body text: Graphite #212121 on light, White on dark with higher line height (\u00a71.2); Callouts: Light Blue 70% tint (data), Golden Sand 30% (text-heavy); Links general: Brand Blue #00529b underline on light, White underline on dark."
